quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  25,61,Bada mutabarrak(ba-barakat) hai woh jisne aasmaan mein burj (fortified spheres) banaye aur us mein ek chiraag aur ek chamakta Chand roshan kiya
  25,62,"Wahi hai jisne raat aur din ko ek dusre ka jaanasheen banaya, har us shaks ke liye jo sabaq lena chahe, ya shukar guzaar hona chahe"
  25,63,Rehman ke (asli) banday woh hai jo zameen par narm chaal chalte hain aur jaahil unke mooh ko aayein to keh detay hain ke tumko salaam
  25,64,Jo apne Rubb ke huzur sajde aur qayaam mein raatein guzarte hain
  25,65,"Jo duaein karte hain ke “Aey hamare Rubb, jahannum ke azaab se humko bacha le, uska azaab to jaan ka laagu hai"
  25,66,Woh to bada hi mustaqar(evil abode) aur muqaam hai”
  25,67,"Jo kharch karte hain to na fizool kharchi karte hain na bukhl, balke unka kharch dono intehaaon (extremes) ke darmiyan aitadaal par qayam rehta hai"
  25,68,"Jo Allah ke siwa kisi aur mabood ko nahin pukarte, Allah ki haraam ki hui kisi jaan ko na-haqq halaak nahin karte, aur na zina (adultery) ke murtakib hotay hain. Yeh kaam jo koi karey woh apne gunaah ka badla payega"
  25,69,Qayamat ke roz usko mukarrar azaab diya jayega aur isi mein woh hamesha zillat ke saath pada rahega
  25,70,"Illa yeh ke koi (in gunaahon ke baad) toubah kar chuka ho aur iman laa kar amal e saleeh karne laga ho, aisey logon ki buraiyon ko Allah bhalaiyon se badal dega aur woh bada gafoor o raheem hai"
  25,71,Jo shaks toubah karke neik amali ikhtiyar karta hai woh to Allah ki taraf palat aata hai jaisa ke palatne ka haqq hai
  25,72,(Aur Rehman ke bandey woh hain) jo jhoot ke gawaah nahin bante aur kisi lagv (fizul/vain) cheez par unka guzar ho jaye to shareef aadmiyon ki tarah guzar jatey hain
  25,73,Jinhein agar unke Rubb ki aayat suna kar naseehat ki jati hai to woh uspar andhey aur behre bankar nahin reh jatey
  25,74,"Jo duaein maanga karte hain ke, “Aey hamare Rubb, humein apni biwiyon aur apni aulaad se aankhon ki thandak de, aur humko parheizgaaron ka imam bana.”"
  25,75,"Yeh hain woh log jo apne sabr ka phal manzil-e-buland ki shakal mein payenge, aadaab o tasleemaat se unka istaqbaal hoga"
  25,76,Woh hamesha hamesha wahan rahenge. Kya hi accha hai woh mustaqar (excellent abode) aur woh muqaam
  25,77,"(Aey Muhammad), logon se kaho, “mere Rubb ko tumhari kya haajat padi hai agar tum usko na pukaro. Ab ke tumne jhutla diya hai, anqareeb woh saza paogey ke jaan chudhani muhaal (never be able to avoid) hogi”"